      <title>新加坡总理将在大选前接管执政党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/singapore-pm-set-to-take-over-ruling-party-ahead-of-next-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡总理黄循财即将执掌执政党人民行动党，在明年大选之前巩固其领导地位。]]></description>
